Package view.dialogs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutNodeDialog
    Pop-up dialog displaying details of the selected node
    AlertDialog
    Simplifies the generation of dialogs.
    AttackerConfigurator
    Shows dialog to configure Attacker (capabilities and passwords/access)
    AttackerConfigurator.Credential  
    AttackerConfigurator.PhysicalAccess  
    AttackerGoalChooser
    Shows dialog to choose attacker goal and specific target
    AttackerListCell
    Modification of JavaFX ListCell, to provide a checkbox and edit and delete buttons on each row
    AttackerSelector
    Dialog to select active attackers, and delete or add attackers
    CountermeasureDialog
    Dialog with all possible and applied countermeasures for the selected node
    CountermeasureDialog.CountermeasurePair  
    DeleteNodeDialog
    Warning message before actual removal of the selected node and its children
    EditNodeDialog
    Dialog to edit the fields of a node
    IDPSelector
    Shows dialog with file chooser to select the input .idp file.
    TreeLoader
    Utility class for the loading functionality of a saved tree.
    TreeSaver
    Utility class for saving functionality.
